qMeasure.qDef:
num(
	IF((license_type_enabled)='Token-based',
	ceil(count({<[Access Type]={'Login Access'},LogTimeStamp= {">=$(=DayStart(today()-6))"}>} distinct UsageId)/10)
    ,Sum({<[License Token Type]={'Analyzer Access'}>} distinct [License Total Tokens])
    )
,'#,##0')
qMeasure.qLabel: Login Tokens or Analyzer Access Used

qMetaDef.description: For Login Access usage, please view this by Month only.
